  "title": "Relief Teacher",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong> Marina Square / Buona Vista, Singapore</p><p><strong>About the Role:</strong><br />We are looking for a reliable and flexible Relief Teacher to join our team. You will assist with teaching and classroom support on an as-needed basis across our Marina Square and Buona Vista centres. This is a great opportunity for someone who enjoys working with children and can step in to ensure smooth classroom operations.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Provide classroom support and cover lessons as assigned</p></li><li><p>Follow lesson plans and school procedures</p></li><li><p>Engage students in learning activities and maintain a positive learning environment</p></li><li><p>Support teachers with administrative or classroom tasks when needed</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Previous teaching or childcare experience preferred</p></li><li><p>Ability to adapt quickly to different classes and schedules</p></li><li><p>Patient, reliable, and enthusiastic about working with children</p></li><li><p>Good communication skills</p></li></ul><p><strong>Perks:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Flexible relief assignments</p></li><li><p>Opportunity to work across multiple centres</p></li><li><p>Friendly and supportive work environment</p></li></ul>",
