    "description": "<p>HWA international school was established in 2006 as the Chinese International School in Singapore, and continues to uphold the global vision that integrates Eastern and Western values, through the International Baccalaureate (IB) philosophy. Our renowned Bilingual and Bicultural program has created an impact on the education system within the IB framework in South East Asia in the last decade. HWA, as an IB school has groomed enablers that have successfully moved on to higher educations. In our continuing effort in impact and bring learning to a higher level, we are seeking professionally trained educators to join HWA's family. &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>",
